Racal Electronics Plc &lt;RCAL.L> announcedthe formation of a new company &lt;Racal-Guardata Inc.> of OrangeCounty California, as well as a co-operative marketingagreement between the new company and &lt;General ElectricInformation Services Company> of the U.S.    Racal said the new company, a part of the Racal-Chubb datasecurity operation, will sell proven data security devices andsystems into the U.S. Where experts believe computer fraudcould be costing users as much as five billions dlrs a year.The agreement enables users of GE's worldwide teleprocessingservices to combat fraud against financial institutions. REUTER&#3;